.TH matrix_avgdwn 3
.SH NAME
matrix_avgdwn \- Calculate the average of each column of a matrix
.SH LIBRARY
matrix (\fIlibmatrix\fR, \fI\-lmatrix\fR)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B #include \[dq]matrix/matrix.h\[dq]
.br
\fBvoid matrix_avgdwn (const Matrix * \fImatrix\fR\fB, Matrix * \fIresult\fR\fB);
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B martix_avgdwn
calculates the average of each column of a matrix \fImatrix\fR, returning the resulting row of values in \fIresult\fR.
.SH SEE ALSO
\fBmatrix_avgrgt\fR(3), \fBmatrix_avgall\fR(3), \fBmatrix\fR(3)
